dct_description_sm: This polygon data represents housing census topics for Cuba in 2012 municipality (municipios). The dataset is part of the East View Global Census Archive published by East View Information Services. Download package includes descriptive metadata, guide with field descriptions, and example questionnaire.
gbl_displayNote_sm: Warning: Restricted to UW-Milwaukee Academic Use only. UWM login required for download.
